🏫 - **1. Go to school...**

🧑‍💻 - **2. Get a job...**

🐀 - **3. Work as a slave until you're 60...**

🪦 - **4. Retire and wait for your death...**

That will be the life, for 99% of you. You can think you are different, you will escape the matrix, you will find a way, etc. etc.

I hate to break it to you, **but this will be your life.**

- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e9dZQelULDk&t

👆🏽 - **Please watch this video and accept the fact that this will be your life.**

*You only got one hope on escaping this cycle, the matrix, the rat race, whatever you wanna call it.*

- **YOU** are the one who needs to take action.
- **YOU** need to sacrifice a few years of comfort, for decades of freedom.
- **YOU** have to put in the work.
- **YOU** have to get rich.
- **YOU** need to network.
- **YOU** need to learn.

It all depends on **YOU.**

The only person who can get you free from this life, the only person who can make you rich, is **you.**

I will give you **2 options**, you can either go back to living this life....

or, **you can escape.**

If you want to escape, live the life of your dreams, have freedom, retire your parents. Head over to:
*-* https://discord.com/channels/1074555785188741220/1107491411940606002

Please watch the video above and read the text.

Then answer my question for you:

*-* *Is this the type of life you wanna live?*
